{"about_the_game":"<i>It's about time!</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/TK_Header_B_01__1_.png?t=1728684597\" /><br>A series of storms approaches the Hourglass Isles. Some people need your aid to weather the lightning, waves, and torrential rain, while others would appreciate help in personal quests. Plan your schedule wisely and make the most of your time\u2014can you balance the demands of the archipelago and ensure everyone gets the help they need?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/tidekeeper_finn_and_chumby.gif?t=1728684597\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/TK_Header_B_02__1_.png?t=1728684597\" /><br>Plan your days to maximize your impact\u2014choose when and where to lend a hand as you balance the needs of the islanders. Earn renown for your helpful deeds, but timing is everything. Can you navigate optimally, arrive on time, and help everyone in need? Your scheduling skills are the key to success!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/tidekeeper_end_of_day_feedback7.gif?t=1728684597\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/TK_Header_B_03__1_.png?t=1728684597\" /><br>Discover hidden paths, secret locations, and new routes as you navigate the Hourglass Isles. Every discovery opens up new opportunities to optimize your travels and complete your schedule more efficiently. Explore to your advantage and make every moment count!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/tidekeeper_loc2.png?t=1728684597\" />     <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst